column5: Just wondering where I can get the freshest roe for sale in or near brantford. Looking to take Hoops 12 out fishing this weekend on some Lake Erie Tribs this weekend, Thanks all
H&H has Roe,   Fishing World in Hamilton does as well.  Or Caledonia Bait and Tackle.  We are hittin up some Erie tribs this weekend as well.  Maybe we will run into you
call lou at silvercreek aquaculture. he has brown and rainbow, but not for much longer, almost gone. 519 833 2559
angling outfitters has some really nice coho from BC in right now. (woodstock)
Fishing Fanatics in Waterloo( a bit of a drive for ya )have trout and salmon roe.  As well as some salmon roe from BC( eggs are much larger ).
